race.description: Signature Shower Screens Stake Cta Division2
race.comment: UTTER MADNESS (7) scored (25.43) last time out at Murray Bridge adding to an already respectable career. Form at the trip sound including four wins. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Great chance to get the job done again. ACE'S CHANCE (5) flew the lids off the inside draw with a fast early split and gave a sight, finishing a 2.25 lengths second (30.66) over 530m at this track. Has a strong record out of this box with four wins and two minor placings from eight starts. Expected to feature. IRON ATLAS (4) tackled far tougher grade latest when finishing 4th over 530m at this track. Won an easier race the start before that at this track. Leading chance. DAKOTA SHINE (2) is worth including.
